<P>
<S ID='S-64' IA='OWN' AZ='OWN'> Note that in Figure <CREF/> the daughter nodes labelled B and D share a common subtree and the subtrees shared between the mother and the B and D daughters appear as siblings in the tree associated with the mother . </S>
</P>
